### Question B (Choice 2 — Alternative) — 14 Marks
**[KTU University Exam — Dec 2023, Adapted]**

**(a)** Explain the **Event Delegation Model** with a neat diagram. List the steps involved in handling a button click event. (7 marks)

**(b)** Write a Java Swing program to create a window with `JCheckBox` items for "Java", "Python", "C++" and a `JButton` labeled "Show Selected". When the button is clicked, display the selected items in a `JLabel`. (7 marks)

