## 4. Structural Diagrams & Schematics

### 4.1 Mermaid Block Diagram: Insertion Operation Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start: insertAtPos function called] --> B{Is list empty?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Set head = newNode]
    C --> Z[Return: Insertion Complete]
    B -- No --> D{Is pos == 1?}
    D -- Yes --> E[newNode.next = head]
    E --> F[head = newNode]
    F --> Z
    D -- No --> G[Initialize temp = head, counter = 1]
    G --> H{counter < pos-1 AND temp.next != NULL?}
    H -- No --> I[Error: Invalid Position]
    I --> Y[Return: Abort]
    H -- Yes --> J[temp = temp.next]
    J --> K[counter = counter + 1]
    K --> H
    H -- Loop ends naturally --> L[newNode.next = temp.next]
    L --> M[temp.next = newNode]
    M --> Z
```

